				<wikidot:authorName>Drewbear</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>301632</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, that's just it. It's <em>NOT</em> a talking animal. It's the person talking to <em>themselves</em>, but the collars modifies that internal dialogue so that the dog <em>APPEARS</em> to be the other voice. There is no actual change in the dog, which presumably continues doing its regular doggy things.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
